OL,3,CMan arrested over social media post
OL,4,Cthreatening to shoot Nigel Farage
OL,6,FA man in his 20s has been arrested
OL,7,Fover an alleged threat to shoot Reform
OL,8,FUK leader Nigel Farage made in a post
OL,9,Fon X.
OL,11,FThe suspect was arrested on Tuesday
OL,12,Fover the social media entry from May,
OL,13,Fahead of the local elections, that
OL,14,Fsaid: "I am going to shoot you in the
OL,15,Fhead if you win", according to the
OL,16,FTelegraph.
OL,18,FFarage formally resigned from
OL,19,FParliament last week, but was the MP
OL,20,Ffor Clacton when the offence allegedly
OL,21,Foccurred.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
