PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784162881
OL,3,CMan arrested over social media post
OL,4,Cthreatening to shoot Nigel Farage
OL,6,FIn a statement on Wednesday, the
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police did not name
OL,8,FFarage, but said: "The arrest relates
OL,9,Fto a social media post from earlier
OL,10,Fthis year, which was reported to
OL,11,Fpolice on Friday, 8 May.
OL,13,F"After receiving the report,
OL,14,Fdetectives submitted an application to
OL,15,Fa social media platform to gain access
OL,16,Fto the user's contact information."
OL,18,FFollowing the initial report, the
OL,19,Fsuspect was arrested at an address in
OL,20,Fsouth London and has since been bailed
OL,21,Fpending further enquiries.
