OL,3,CMan arrested over social media post
OL,4,Cthreatening to shoot Nigel Farage
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FNews of the arrest came days after the
OL,12,Fdeath of Ann Widdecombe, a Reform
OL,13,Fspokesperson and former Conservative
OL,14,Fminister who was found dead in her
OL,15,Fhome having suffered serious injuries.
OL,17,FA murder investigation is underway
OL,18,Finto her death, which counter-
OL,19,Fterrorism police have called a
OL,20,F"targeted attack".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
