PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784162881
OL,3,CMan arrested over social media post
OL,4,Cthreatening to shoot Nigel Farage
OL,6,FPolice said they are investigating
OL,7,Fwhether the suspect had wanted to
OL,8,Ftarget Reform UK MPs, and figures from
OL,9,Facross the political spectrum have
OL,10,Fraised concerns about the safety of
OL,11,Fcurrent and former MPs and members of
OL,12,Fother parties.
OL,14,FFarage told the Daily Telegraph he has
OL,15,Ffaced multiple threats on social media
OL,16,F"for years".
