OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784162881
OL,3,CMan arrested over social media post
OL,4,Cthreatening to shoot Nigel Farage
OL,6,FHe said: "This is the first time the
OL,7,Fpolice have ever proactively acted on
OL,8,Fa social media post, and I hope they
OL,9,Fare looking at the other three or four
OL,10,Fhundred similar posts from this year
OL,11,Falone."
OL,13,FIn recent days, questions have been
OL,14,Fraised over MP safety, with Reform's
OL,15,Fhome affairs spokesperson Zia Yusuf
OL,16,Fclaiming "none of the Government, the
OL,17,FSpeaker, nor the police care at all
OL,18,Fabout the security of Reform MPs".
OL,26,@nD@JOUxD@JOU
