CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784162881
OL,3,CMan arrested over social media post
OL,4,Cthreatening to shoot Nigel Farage
OL,6,FIncoming prime minister Andy Burnham
OL,7,Fhas said there needs to be a "serious
OL,8,Freview" into MPs' security following
OL,9,Fthe suspected murder of Widdecombe.
OL,11,FSpeaking on Tuesday, Burnham said
OL,12,Fpolitics had "darkened" since he was
OL,13,Flast in Westminster and that
OL,14,Fprotections may need to be "increased
OL,15,Ffurther".
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
